reviewText: I enjoyed seeing these ads after many years & now introducing my Canadian husband to the infamous Schultz & Dooley. The video brought back good times as I remembered sitting around the TV with my brothers & sisters & laughing away at latest antics of Schultz & Dooley. We used to love looking forward to the newest ads, wondering what the boys were up to. These were funny & engaging ads - ones we talked about with our friends at school. They were the superbowl ads in the days before there was a superbowl!
